kobe_explore

library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
df <- read.csv('~/kaggle/kobe/data.csv')

df$shot_made_flag <- factor(df$shot_made_flag, level = c('1', '0'))

train <- df[!is.na(df$shot_made_flag), ]
test <- df[is.na(df$shot_made_flag), ]
ggacc <- function(feature) {
  ggplot(
    train, 
    aes_string(
      paste0('x = ', feature)
      )
    ) +
    geom_bar(
      aes(fill = shot_made_flag), 
      stat = 'count', 
      position = 'fill',
      color = 'black'
    )
}
